* 0.00975884 BTC worth about $412 was sent to GiveDirectly (address 34kwsubU6ExhXJdTfdNN1CHYyPvfHajFnX) from our Coinbase account as described in this [transaction](https://www.blockchain.com/explorer/transactions/btc/d17248b3b3a37bae688c234615ce846ad6076a0a3e4cfc4407a52c59c2020cf3). Note that this tx also contains other outputs.

