* 15.149438665 ETH were sent to GiveDirectly (address 0x750EF1D7a0b4Ab1c97B7A623D7917CcEb5ea779C) from our  wallet as described in this [transaction](https://etherscan.io/tx/0x37939481c528ac81aaceb865497840dfa08d441bac1fcc724e031b6ddb1ee9a0). 

The board and officers were reluctant to dissolve. We are very grateful to those who have contributed in any way to the foundation.  We still plan to act as individuals to fulfill the mission of the foundation:  promote decentralizing technology, educate the world on its potential, and fund research to improve it. 
